name: Imperium Naturae (Titouan CADORET)
description:
Imperium Naturae is a game that I was able to develop during my first year of study within a team of 8 peoples. During the production of the project, I was notably able to be in charge of Programming as well as Integration within the 3D Unity engine. But I was also able to work on the Level Design of the different levels of the game.

Credits : 3D Modeling & Animation : BRUNEAU Jade, DEJEAN Antoine, ELISABETH Anouck, GAUDICHON Erwan, LE BEAU Gwen, MANCEAU Gensana, PICHON Antonin Programmation & Integration : DEJEAN Antoine, CADORET Titouan Level Design : CADORET Titouan Game Design : CREPEL Justine, LE BEAU Gwen
